# Force LF line endings for files that need them regardless of the
# author's platform. GitHub Actions records a startup_failure on
# every push for any workflow committed with CRLF terminators, so the
# whole .github/ tree is pinned to LF. Shell scripts and Unix config
# files match for the same reason. Everything else falls back to Git's
# auto-detection.

.github/workflows/*.yml text eol=lf
.github/workflows/*.yaml text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
